statement that the U.S. allegations written in the six-page report
of the White House "do not stand on solid bases."
</P>
<P>
It is reported that the U.S. government recently submitted a
six-page report to the Congress, which accuses Iraq of continuing
to develop weapons of mass destruction. (BC-Iraq-US Allegations)

