<HEADLINE> Xinhua Photo List for September 7 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 7 (Xinhua)-- Following is the photo list for
September 7 released by Xinhua.
1. 11-year-old Deng Xuejian, who used to weigh 174.25 kilos goes
back to school again.
2. A brand new type Hongqi car is on display at an exhibition held
in Changchun.
3. Jia Qinglin, secretary of the Beijing Municipal Committee of
the Communist Party of China, unveils the plate of Beijing 2008
Olympic Bid Committee.
4. A middle school teacher coaches his students in experiment.
5. The Lunqian No.1 well squirts crude oil in Lunpola Basin in
north Tibet.
6. Chinese Defence Minister Chi Haotian meets with Jiri Sedivy,
visiting chief of General Staff of the armed forces of the Czech
Republic in Beijing.
7. Chinese Vice-President Hu Jintao meets with visiting Kuwaiti
Deputy Prime Minister and Defense Minister Sheik Salem Sabah Al-
Salem Al-Sabah in Beijing.
8. The director-general of the International Bureau of the UPU and
vice-president of the Chinese Organizing Committee of the ongoing
22nd Universal Postal Congress unveils the bronze plaque at a
grand ceremony to mark the 125th anniversary of the founding of
UPU.
