is is rather important to us," Agassi said. "Based on the last few
weeks of conversation, it seems to me like, so far every time has
been made really aware of the concerns, she has managed to take
steps toward remedying any particular concern."
</P>
<P>
McEnroe, 40, holds several U.S. Davis Cup records: years on
team (12), team matches won (30), singles matches played (49),
combined matches played (69) and won (59). 
