the fourth annual conference and General Assembly of the
International Association of Prosecutors in Beijing.
</P>
<P>
Han also met today with U Tha Dun, attorney general of Myanmar,
Heloise Rozenblad, attorney-general of Surinam, Bart Katureebe,
attorney-general of Uganda, Daniel Bellemare, assistant deputy
attorney-general of Canada, Mircea Criste, prosecutor-general of
Romania, and Mohammad Farooq Chaudhry, attorney-general of
Pakistan.  
