</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 26 degrees C., max. 33 degrees C., cloudy to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 26 degrees C., max. 32 degrees C., cloudy to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Macao: min. 25 degrees C., max. 32 degrees C., cloudy to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze. 
