rejuvenation facilities.
</P>
<P>
A total of 102 buyers, mainly global travel agents
specializing in health and recreational packages, have already
arrived in Bangkok and are now touring the country's spas, herbal
treatment centers, meditation retreats and hospitals, a TAT press
release said Tuesday.
</P>
