quoted as saying that the authority is quite optimistic that the
mart will help attract people all around the world to come to
Thailand and get medical treatment at a fraction of the price in
other countries.
</P>
<P>
The mart will also help promote the home-grown traditions of
Thailand, such as Thai massage, herbal treatment and various other
forms of preventive and curative treatment, he said. 
