<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, September 7 (Xinhua) -- Share prices on the Kuala
Lumpur Stock Exchange closed lower Tuesday on mild profit taking
by retailers, but losses were well cushioned by some support on
selected blue chips.
</P>
