</P>
<P>
-- Israeli President Ezer Weizman and Prime Minister Ehud
Barak phoned Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak on Monday to inquire
about his health after Monday's assassination attempt against
him. Mubarak told Weizman that he was healthy.
</P>
<P>
