CANBERRA -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin arrived here Tuesday
to continue his state visit to Australia.
</P>
<P>
Jiang's plane landed at 5:10 p.m. local time (0710 GMT) at the
Royal Australian Air Force Base, where Australian Governor-General
William Deane and his wife Helen Deane, and Australian Prime
Minister John Howard and his wife Janette Howard greeted Jiang and
his wife Wang Yeping. (Australia-Jiang-Arrival) 
</P>
