scientists and technicians to establish ventures in the high-tech
zones and the government has a regulation to encourage scientific
research institutes, universities, and scientists to open high-
tech ventures.
</P>
<P>
The government has also established a fund for technology-based
small and medium sized high-tech ventures with a one billion yuan
allocation at the start. Another 2 billion yuan will also be
provided for high-tech ventures.
</P>
